'''白鹭'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Egretta garzetta''}}），又称'''-{zh-cn:小白鹭;zh-tw:白鷺;}-'''<ref name="McCarthy2006">{{cite book|author=Eugene M. McCarthy|title=Handbook of Avian Hybrids of the World|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pgESDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA190|date=16 February 2006|publisher=Oxford University Press, USA|isbn=978-0-19-518323-8|pages=190–|access-date=2019-04-11|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109062638/https://books.google.com/books?id=pgESDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA190|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[白鹭属|白鹭属]]的一個種。

== 特徵 ==
体长约56cm，全身白羽，交偶期間枕部垂有兩條細長翎作為飾羽，背和上胸部分披蓬松蓑羽，期後消失。細長黑[[鳥喙|喙]]；黑腿，黄脚掌；叫聲：繁殖巢群中發出嘎嘎嘎叫聲。<ref name="著2016">{{cite book|author=李惠綿 著|title=中原音韻箋釋|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2SBIDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA643|date=5 January 2016|publisher=國立臺灣大學出版中心|isbn=978-986-350-137-4|pages=643–|access-date=2019-04-11|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109061109/https://books.google.com/books?id=2SBIDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA643|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 分佈 ==
春夏多活动于湖沼岸边、水田、河岸、沙滩、泥滩及沿海小溪流，成散群出現<ref name="刘亚玲1988">{{cite book|author=刘亚玲|title=中国历代诗歌鉴赏辞典|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oCstAQAAIAAJ|year=1988|publisher=中国民间文艺出版社}}</ref>。分布于非洲、欧洲、亚洲及大洋洲，在中国主要见于[[长江|长江]]以南各地和[[海南岛|海南岛]]，在中部地区多为[[候鸟|候鸟]]，南方大多为[[留鸟|留鸟]]。<ref name="王继权姚国华1982">{{cite book|author1=王继权|author2=姚国华|author3=徐培均|title=郭沫若旧体诗词系年注釋|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VshsAAAAIAAJ|year=1982|publisher=黑龙江人民出版社|access-date=2019-04-11|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109061119/https://books.google.com/books?id=VshsAAAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref> 台灣也普遍可見。

== 食物 ==
[[鱼|鱼]]、甲壳动物和[[昆虫|昆虫]]。以各式魚蝦為主食，覓食時會用一隻腳在水中擾動。<ref name="廖本興2012">{{cite book|author=廖本興|title=台灣野鳥圖鑑水鳥篇|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XwSGDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT104|year=2012|publisher=晨星出版|isbn=978-986-177-564-7|pages=104–|access-date=2019-04-11|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109061124/https://books.google.com/books?id=XwSGDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT104|dead-url=no}}</ref>

